headline: The Estée Lauder Companies Holds Annual Meeting of Stockholders
summary: NEW YORK, November 08, 2024--The Estée Lauder Companies Inc. (NYSE: EL) held its Annual Meeting of Stockholders today. William P. Lauder, Executive Chairman, chaired the meeting.

headline: No Guidance, Poor Result, And Management Shake Up Is Scaring Away Estee Lauder (EL) Investors
summary: The recently announced financials of The Estee Lauder Companies Inc. unveil significant financial strain stemming from macroeconomic challenges in China and the Asian travel sector market. Management is unsure how long it will take the Chinese market to recover. Considering these factors and the dividend cut, it seems best to stay away from the company’s […]

headline: Q3 Rundown: Estée Lauder (NYSE:EL) Vs Other Personal Care Stocks
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q3. Today, we are looking at personal care stocks, starting with Estée Lauder (NYSE:EL).
